These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, october, june, august, september, december
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, animation, documentary, sports, drama, zombie
1. the person watching epic movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching drama movies##2
5. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
6. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
7. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
8. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching documentary movies##1
9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Birthday         | september     | june | april | august | december      | october |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | drama  | epic    | zombie | documentary | animation    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
6 different games are played: chess, billiard, whist, backgammon, scrabble, bridge
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, lemonade, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, fanta
 1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person playing whist is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Game   | chess  | backgammon  | scrabble | billiard   | bridge | whist |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk | sprite    | fanta | milk   | hot-chocolate   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  photographer, analyst, writer, dancer, freelancer, entrepreneur
House: palace, tower, wooden, ranch-style, craftsman, townhouse
1. the palace house is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the writer is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
3. the wooden house is on the left or right of the writer##3
4. the dancer is in an odd position##4
5. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the dancer##3
6. the freelancer is on the left or right of the palace house##3
7. the tower house is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
9. the ranch-style house is the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Job   | photographer    | freelancer | writer     | analyst         | dancer       | entrepreneur     |
| House         | palace | wooden  | tower | townhouse | craftsman | ranch-style |

