.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily, bellflower, poppy, amaryllis, daffodil
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: reggae, jazz, electronic, pop, soul, r&b
1. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
4. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
5. the fan of electronic is the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
9. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Flower   | marigold | lily     | bellflower     | poppy | amaryllis | daffodil |
| Music-Genre     | r&b    | jazz | electronic | pop  | soul       | reggae      |

