.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: emerald, purple, yellow, light-blue, lavender, orange
City: hamburg, prague, venice, london, berlin, paris
 1. the person traveling to london is between the person who likes yellow and the person traveling to venice##2
 2. the person who likes purple is the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
10. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
11. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
12. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Color   | lavender | light-blue | emerald | orange    | yellow    | purple |
| City     | prague         | hamburg       | venice  | london | berlin | paris   |

