.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, milk, lemonade, tea, cola
There 6 different types of food: apricot, garlic, pepper, cabbage, orange, mango
 1. the person eating garlic is the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 3. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating cabbage##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating mango is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea   | lemonade    | cola    | juice  | mirinda   |
| Food   | mango | pepper | cabbage | apricot | orange | garlic |

