 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
10. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

