.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-8::.
6 different games are played: monopoly, go, canasta, poker, snooker, whist
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, filmmaking, photography, traveling, dancing
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |    3     |       4       |     5      |      6       |
| Game   | monopoly | canasta     | go | whist         | snooker        | poker       |
| Hobby      | filmmaking       | photography | collecting  | dancing | traveling | rock-climbing |

