.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-9::.
6 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, snake, guinea-pig, hedgehog, frog
House: farmhouse, modern, victorian, wooden, art-deco, townhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
2. the modern house is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
5. the townhouse house is between the owner of the snake and the victorian house##2
6. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the townhouse house##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4       |   5    |     6     |
| Pet   | frog | snake       | goat     | hedgehog     | guinea-pig  | goldfish    |
| House      | wooden | farmhouse | townhouse | victorian | modern | art-deco |

