.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, thriller, animation, horror, disaster, fantasy
6 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, rabbit, snake, fish, turtle
 1. the owner of the snake is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
 2. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 6. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 9. the person watching family movies is the owner of the fish##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Movie-Genre    | family | horror | animation | fantasy | disaster      | thriller    |
| Pet   | fish       | turtle      | hedgehog     | snake  | bird | rabbit |

