 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the dunhill-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in august and the bongani-smoker##2
 6. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is the game-smoker##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |       4       |     5      |    6    |
