.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, singing, collecting, reading, sudoku
6 different games are played: whist, canasta, chess, go, poker, bridge
 1. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing go##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person playing poker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
 8. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing whist is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person playing canasta##2
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
12. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Hobby   | traveling    | singing      | collecting  | reading  | sudoku           | magic-tricks  |
| Game    | poker | canasta | whist | go | bridge | chess |

 